1. [Node JS] (https://nodejs.org/en/)
    $ npm version
2. [git] (https://git-scm.com/downloads)
  * select option "Use Git and optional Unix tools from the Windows Cammand Prompt"
    $ git
3. Codova CLI and Ionic Framework
  $ npm install -g cordova
  $ npm install -g ionic
  $ ionic
